<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 18:09:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>当以色列准备打击真主党时，西方努力避免黎巴嫩爆发全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，全面战争的威胁取决于真主党对以色列袭击黎巴嫩的反应。美国和法国正试图阻止以色列以贝鲁特或其他主要城市为目标，以报复迈季代勒沙姆斯袭击事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 296 天：外交官称正在努力阻止以色列袭击贝鲁特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</link><description>数千人参加真主党在德鲁兹镇火箭弹袭击中丧生的 12 名儿童和青少年的葬礼 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特表示真主党将付出沉重代价 ■ 伊朗警告以色列不要在黎巴嫩进行任何“新冒险” ■ 据报道真主党清理了前方的关键地点以色列的预期反应 ■ 这是战争进入 296 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</guid></item><item><title>这些久经沙场的以色列和美国退伍军人如何希望结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-these-battle-hardened-israeli-and-u-s-veterans-hope-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-f9b0-d10b-a3b8-fdf01c5e0000</link><description>在一项新的合作中，来自以色列“打破沉默”组织和“美国共同防御”组织的前士兵们正在宣扬他们的信念，即退伍军人拥有理解和反对不公正现象的独特能力：“我们去过那里，知道我们在谈论什么，所以人们倾向于倾听&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-these-battle-hardened-israeli-and-u-s-veterans-hope-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-f9b0-d10b-a3b8-fdf01c5e0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列军队在加沙南部深入推进；据报道20人死亡，数千人逃离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</link><description>随着以色列撤离命令促使更多人离开加沙中部和南部，以色列坦克开进了汗尤尼斯。以色列国防军表示，一名军官和一名士兵在加沙南部的战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 15:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</guid></item><item><title>“笨拙”但沉重：真主党在迈季代勒沙姆斯发射伊朗制造的火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</link><description>Falaq 1于20世纪90年代在伊朗研制，旨在为军队提供重型火箭炮，能够打击掩体和其他目标，在叙利亚内战期间，它被真主党和叙利亚军队使用。自一月份以来，真主党已向以色列发射了数十次火箭</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</guid></item><item><title>如果美国不否决对以色列的制裁怎么办？法律专家称“这是世界末日”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</link><description>犹太人民政策研究所副所长舒基·弗里德曼表示，对定居者实施制裁的影响不仅限于约旦河西岸，而且已经在削弱以色列的国际合法性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的德鲁兹社区解释说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</link><description>以色列德鲁兹人正在哀悼在黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击戈兰高地期间丧生的 11 名儿童。这个紧密团结的社区在以色列军事和社会中发挥着关键作用，但在这些问题上也存在分歧。谁是德鲁兹人，他们与中东各地社区的关系如何，最近的战争对他们有何影响？</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列与哈马斯人质停火协议将包括外国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</link><description>据以色列军方称，有 10 名外国人在加沙地带被扣为人质，其中 7 人还活着。 ■ 警方还在调查一名自 10 月 7 日以来一直失踪的泰国公民的案件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 11:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</guid></item><item><title>一位面临所有困难的跨巴勒斯坦妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</link><description>纪录片《她的名字叫泽哈瓦》去年在海法电影节上获得了著名奖项，但战争意味着它必须等待才能重返大银幕</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部11名儿童被杀，但内塔尼亚胡并不着急</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</link><description>一个正在“七条战线”作战并出国旅行一周（包括一次特别的周末停留）的国家的元首根本不是一个领导人。他会的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加以色列北部真主党火箭袭击中丧生的儿童和青少年的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</link><description>10 名遇难者被埋葬在真主党火箭周六袭击的 Majdal Shams ■ 另一名遇难者被安葬在恩钦亚 ■ 28 人仍在医院接受治疗</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 06:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-and-teens-killed-in-north-israel-rocket-strike-to-be-laid-to-rest/00000190-f7ed-d469-a39d-f7ff90670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布一周前被反坦克火力击伤的约纳坦·阿哈龙·格林布拉特中士死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/00000190-f7ca-d469-a39d-f7df6c950000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡召集内阁讨论黎巴嫩罢工；以色列发布新的加沙撤离令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</link><description>报道：以色列在黎巴嫩的报复“肯定”，避免袭击贝鲁特的谈判正在进行中 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室寻求会见一些 Majdal Shams 遇难者家属，但遭到拒绝 ■ 黎巴嫩中东航空公司将部分航班从周日晚间推迟到周一上午，但没有上榜原因 ■ 以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙南部受重伤 ■ 真主党火箭弹袭击以色列 Majdal Shams，造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 02:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-live/u-s-condemns-horrific-attack-reportedly-highly-concerned-over-all-out-war/00000190-f724-d469-a39d-f7b7cff70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿的胜利并不能抵消他的惨重损失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡在椭圆形办公室合影并在国会获得掌声，但许多关键问题仍未解决——尤其是人质交易——并且与卡马拉·哈里斯爆发了激烈的争执</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 23:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wins-in-washington-dont-cancel-out-his-heavy-losses/00000190-f66b-d541-adbc-fffb226c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党比以往任何时候都更接近全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</link><description>周六，以色列在北部玩的俄罗斯轮盘赌在马贾勒沙姆斯失败了，当时真主党对以色列对其特工的袭击做出了回应。由于坚持延长华盛顿之行，内塔尼亚胡总理只能远程参加防务磋商</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-risks-full-scale-escalation-with-hezbollah-while-still-wrangling-on-gaza-front/00000190-f5cb-dda7-a9f7-f7ff03d80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：真主党将付出前所未有的代价；最高部长呼吁暗杀纳斯鲁拉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</link><description>真主党否认对以色列北部德鲁兹城镇发动致命袭击负责，该袭击造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡。白宫谴责这起“可怕”的袭击，而以色列北部当地领导人要求立即采取军事回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:57:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/netanyahu-hezbollah-will-pay-unprecedented-price-top-minister-calls-to-kill-nasrallah/00000190-f5ca-d8b8-a59a-fdde66be0000</guid></item><item><title>“孩子们来玩，爆炸将他们撕成碎片”：目击者讲述了令人痛心的 Majdal Shams 袭击事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</link><description>到达导致 11 名儿童和青少年死亡的罢工现场的 Majdal Shams 和附近村庄的居民报告说，爆炸发生在警报响起几秒钟后。地上有受伤和死亡的儿童。这让我想起了 10 月 7 日。”一位居民说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/children-came-to-play-and-an-explosion-shredded-them-to-pieces/00000190-f596-d8b8-a59a-fd9e0e080000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击以色列戈兰高地，造成 11 名儿童和青少年死亡；以色列国防军指责真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</link><description>以色列医疗部门表示，此次袭击袭击了一个正在玩耍的儿童足球场，共有 29 人受伤。以色列国防军指责真主党发动了这次袭击，此前以色列对四名特工发动了袭击。现场的一名医生回忆道，“所有受害者都是 8 至 14 岁的儿童，都穿着运动服”</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/11-children-teens-killed-and-dozens-wounded-in-rocket-strike-on-majdal-shams/00000190-f54a-d298-a592-fd7bffe80000</guid></item><item><title>法院以“危害安全”为由延长半岛电视台在以色列的广播禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</link><description>该禁令是根据议会五月通过的一项法律发布的，该法律允许半岛电视台停止从以色列进行广播。法官表示，他已经看到证据证明该电视台播放的内容煽动恐怖袭击</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 18:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/court-extends-al-jazeera-broadcasting-ban-in-israel-citing-harm-to-security/00000190-f54f-d541-adbc-fdffd24b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸纳布卢斯巴勒斯坦武装分子，17岁青年被打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</link><description>军方表示，纳布卢斯巴拉塔难民营的袭击目标是武装武装分子，造成一人死亡、多人受伤。以色列安全部门消息人士称，这是对当天早上针对以色列国防军士兵的枪击事件的回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-drone-targets-palestinian-militants-in-west-banks-nablus-17-year-old-killed/00000190-f527-d45d-a5b3-ffaf9d060000</guid></item></channel></rss>